 Page Converter. This will allow you to know the total number of pages your=
 article occupies based on the font and spacing you=E2=80=99ll be using, an=
d of course, the word count. This little tool is perfect for assignments wh=
ere your instructor just requires minimum or maximum pages.</span></p><h3><=
strong>More About Word Count</strong></h3><p><span style=3D"font-weight: 40=
0;">With a name like Word Count Tool, we=E2=80=99re all about the word coun=
t. Aside from our word counter, we also publish many works that talk about =
