ake sure to click the box beside =E2=80=9Cdisplay word count while typing,=
=E2=80=9D and a word counter will show at the bottom of your screen.</span>=
</p><h3><strong>Where To Find Word Count On Microsoft Word?</strong></h3><p=
><span style=3D"font-weight: 400;">If you prefer using the classic Microsof=
t Word to write, then no worries. <a href=3D"https://www.wordcounttool.com/=
