Show Word Count.=E2=80=9D If you also want to see character count or paragr=
aph count, hover the pointer over the right side of the counter and click o=
n the arrows that appear to select which counter you want to display. And t=
here you go.</span></p><h3><strong>How To Increase Word Count?</strong></h3=
><p><span style=3D"font-weight: 400;">A lot of times, we have trouble reach=
