 We=E2=80=99ve all been there. But, if your professor is asking for a certa=
in number of words, you have to meet that else get deductions. Well, don=E2=
=80=99t worry because there are ways to increase your word count. One of th=
e best ways to achieve a lengthier piece is by adding examples. Deliver you=
r point well by illustrating a scenario. This way, your readers can easily =
grasp your concept and also meet the required word count.&nbsp;</span></p><=
h3><strong>How To Decrease Word Count?</strong></h3><p><span style=3D"font-=
