ong=E2=80=9D and miss the opportunity of a new adventure. But for book love=
rs out there, there is no greater joy than to dive into a wondrous new worl=
d. And often, you get so caught up in the story that you don=E2=80=99t even=
 realize the length of what you=E2=80=99ve already read. If you=E2=80=99re =
